To build and run
###################
java -jar converter.jar <absolute path of JSON file> <absolute path of XML file>

Libraries used:
#################
gson-2.8.6.jar (https://jar-download.com/artifacts/com.google.code.gson/gson/2.8.6)

####
The code design is based on the peeking each element of the JSON and 
checking the token using GSON jar utility for various cases like begin object, end object, Begin array etc